<mjml>
  <mj-body>
    <mj-section padding-top="48px" padding-bottom="24px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-image
          href="https://axyscreative.com/"
          src="https://axyscreative.com/public/email-logo.png"
          alt=""
          width="200px"
        >
        </mj-image>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section padding="24px">
      <mj-column
        background-color="#F0F0F0"
        border-radius="8px"
        padding="16px 4px"
      >
        <mj-text font-size="20px" color="#E48C66" align="left">
          Admin Permissions Expiring Soon
        </mj-text>
        <mj-spacer height="12px" />
        <mj-text color="#101010" line-height="24px" font-size="15px">
          Hey [site admins], we noticed your subscription has been paused â€”
          totally understandable!
          <strong>Please note</strong> however, that access to the admin
          dashboard for
          <a href="mailto:help@axyscreative.com" style="color: #e48c66"
            >[site url]</a
          >
          will <strong>expire on [date]</strong>, the end of your original
          subscription billing period.
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text color="#101010" line-height="24px" font-size="15px">
          To continue using this feature you can either resume your [current]
          plan or move to our
          <a
            href="https://buy.stripe.com/bIYaFu2nT2ne7sc5kp"
            style="color: #e48c66"
            >Admin Plan</a
          >, originally priced at $150/month, now available for a limited 20%
          discount at $120/month.
          <strong>Offer ends [date, 60 days].</strong>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text color="#101010" line-height="24px" font-size="15px">
          If you'd rather let it go for now, no worries, you can always sign on
          in the future!
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text color="#101010" line-height="24px" font-size="15px">
          If you have any questions about changing your subscription or need to
          resume your plan, feel free to reach us at
          <a href="mailto:help@axyscreative.com" style="color: #e48c66">
            help@axyscreative.com
          </a>
          . You can also visit your Stripe account to view billing info.
        </mj-text>
        <mj-button
          href="https://billing.stripe.com/p/login/bIYcNw7NXeQDchi000"
          background-color="#E48C66"
          align="left"
          font-size="15px"
          padding="12px 24px"
        >
          Visit Account Portal
        </mj-button>
        <mj-spacer height="24px" />
        <mj-text font-size="15px" color="#E48C66">
          Aaron,
          <br /><br />
          AXYS Creative
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section padding="0">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text
          color="#101010"
          line-height="24px"
          font-size="13px"
          align="center"
        >
          <em>
            This email was sent regarding your subscription with
            <a href="https://axyscreative.com" style="color: #e48c66">
              axyscreative.com
            </a>
          </em>
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section padding="12px 0">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text
          align="center"
          font-size="13px"
          color="#101010"
          font-family="helvetica"
        >
          Connect with us:
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text align="center">
          <a
            href="https://www.instagram.com/axyscreative/"
            style="margin-right: 12px; color: transparent"
          >
            <img
              src="https://axyscreative.com/public/email-link-instagram.png"
              alt="Instagram"
              width="36px"
              style="display: inline"
            />
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://dribbble.com/axyscreative"
            style="margin-right: 12px; color: transparent"
          >
            <img
              src="https://axyscreative.com/public/email-link-dribbble.png"
              alt="Dribbble"
              width="36px"
              style="display: inline"
            />
          </a>
          <a href="https://x.com/AXYSCreative">
            <img
              src="https://axyscreative.com/public/email-link-twitter-x.png"
              alt="Twitter/X"
              width="36px"
              style="display: inline"
            />
          </a>
        </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
  </mj-body>
</mjml>
